School Culture

VERY FRIENDLY locals who love exchange students, good amt of partying and raves.

Attendance Levels

You can miss up to 6 classes.

Exam Policies

Different kinds of exams hahaha but the ones i did were mostly MCQ.

Modules offered

MKT etc.

I took MKT mods, unsure about the rest.

Location

Not too far from downtown

Getting Around

Free public transport for students!!! However, as the city is pretty big, u would need a car to rly travel around a lot‚Ä¶ my tip is to make local friends with cars >:)

Cost of Living

Groceries are affordable, so I usually cook and eat at home! Eating out is expensive üôÅ

I stayed in a house on campus, as it was the best way to make friends!
